com.apigee.sdk.data.client.entities
Class Entity

java.lang.Object
  com.apigee.sdk.data.client.entities.Entity
Direct Known Subclasses:
Activity, Device, Group, Message, User
public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object

Models an entity of any type as a local object. Type-specific classes are extended from this class.

See Also:
API BaaS data model documentation
